181
00:12:50,818 --> 00:12:52,778
Kenapa tak sepenting itu?

182
00:12:53,529 --> 00:12:55,239
Kau tak bisa terus melajang.

183
00:12:57,491 --> 00:12:59,243
Bahkan ada yang mencampakkan anaknya,

184
00:12:59,326 --> 00:13:01,037
