Tentu. Tak perlu khawatir.

191
00:13:22,767 --> 00:13:25,269
- Kalau begitu, aku pergi.
- Eun-u bilang apa?

192
00:13:25,352 --> 00:13:27,271
Biarkan dia pulang.

193
00:13:28,773 --> 00:13:30,149
Pulanglah, Ji-ho.

194
00:13:46,665 --> 00:13:47,958
Aku kembali di akhir pekan.

195
00:13:48,501 --> 00:13:51,003
Jalani kehidupanmu.
Tak perlu selalu kemari.

196
00:13:51,420 --> 00:13:54,382
Aku sedang senggang.
Kabari aku jika ada apa-apa.

197
00:13:55,341 --> 00:13:57,218
Ibumu dan ayah belum setua itu.

198
00:13:58,511 --> 00:13:59,720
Jangan lupa makan, ya.

199
00:14:02,181 --> 00:14:03,182
Tak akan.

200
00:14:04,141 --> 00:14:05,184
Selamat malam.

201
00:14:36,674 --> 00:14:38,217
Kau si apoteker, 'kan?

202
00:14:40,010 --> 00:14:41,178
