203
00:14:41,804 --> 00:14:43,055
Ya, di lantai tiga.

204
00:14:44,265 --> 00:14:47,268
Begitu, ya.

205
00:14:48,310 --> 00:14:49,478
Menarik.

206
00:14:52,815 --> 00:14:54,358
