528
00:42:23,338 --> 00:42:25,632
Aku harus pergi sebelum dia pulang.

529
00:42:27,425 --> 00:42:28,885
Kenapa kau begitu membencinya?

530
00:42:32,097 --> 00:42:33,556
Dia tak tahu cara mencintaimu.

531
00:42:39,896 --> 00:42:41,481
Aku mau buat kopi.

532
00:42:49,030 --> 00:42:52,742
