kau harus kencan lagi.

581
00:46:09,939 --> 00:46:11,065
Aku tak mau apa-apa.

582
00:46:12,775 --> 00:46:14,277
Kau harus pikirkan Eun-u juga.

583
00:46:17,530 --> 00:46:19,449
Aku tak mau cari pengasuh.

584
00:46:21,492 --> 00:46:22,535
