604
00:48:04,762 --> 00:48:06,180
Aku sedang berjalan pulang.

605
00:48:10,643 --> 00:48:11,811
Kau baru pulang kerja?

606
00:48:12,395 --> 00:48:13,563
Tidak, bersama temanku.

607
00:48:14,856 --> 00:48:16,607
