609
00:48:22,780 --> 00:48:25,241
<i>Omong-omong, kenapa menelepon?</i>

610
00:48:28,536 --> 00:48:30,872
Aku kebetulan melihatmu saat pulang

611
00:48:32,165 --> 00:48:33,749
